<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1899816-the-above-review-states-this-was-the-only">The above review states this was the only leper colony in the US. Years ago I read a book about a hospital in I believe Louisiana devoted to leprosy. It to was very good, unfortunately I don’t recall the name. I lived in Honolulu at the time so was familiar with Father Damian and Molokai . So is Molokai really that only leper colony in the US? Maybe the difference is between colony and hospital?</a>
